labels.label: Call API for forecasts and load to hive

entry.value: SELECT id, id_airport, name, latitude_deg, longitude_deg from flowfile
SELECT id, dt, tstamp from flowfile
SELECT id, temp, weather_description, wind_speed, pop from flowfile

select concat(f.tstamp, f.id_airport, f.dt) as id, f.id_airport,f.dt, f.tstamp, f.temp,f.weather_description,f.wind_speed,f.pop,a.name,a.latitude_deg,a.longitude_deg from (SELECT * FROM (SELECT * FROM forecasts WHERE month=from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(), "MM-YYYY")) h WHERE h.tstamp > (unix_timestamp() - (10 * 60 * 100))) f join airports a on f.id_airport = a.id

LOAD DATA INPATH '/user/airports_project/${filename}' OVERWRITE INTO TABLE forecasts_staging; SET mapreduce.framework.name=local; SET hive.exec.dynamic.partition=true; SET hive.exec.dynamic.partition.mode=non-strict; SET hive.enforce.bucketing=true; INSERT INTO forecasts PARTITION(month) SELECT * from forecasts_staging
